{"tid":1399723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（學術討論）警察可否接管受罷工影響的政府部門及交通運輸","createTime":"2019-08-03T09:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T11:56:18.000Z","uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"497ebf2f6613a7c3d9ae2d1d377cd31214c1a4e3","tid":1399723,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:17:13.000Z","msg":"今日警察記者會對網上有人呼籲罷工感到遺憾。其實警察在緊急情況，可否接管交通運輸同各政府部門、傳媒，監督員工繼續工作，以協助恢復交通及公共服務的秩序？<br />\n例如某巴士公司有大量司機罷工，警察可否安排交通警協助駕駛巴士俾想返工嘅人返工？警察可否派公關部警察去電台負責發放警察新聞？派警察去税局負責收税？如有AO罷工，派高級警官去政府總部替代其職務，負責政府行政決策。大家點睇？"},{"pid":"7ad5ad6891d449dd353fc4b25959ae8deb0b7e5d","tid":1399723,"uid":83487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 真的香港人"},{"pid":"4bc8f0c813b538764e748279f48a2b956776e037","tid":1399723,"uid":221055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:21:04.000Z","msg":"on 99 <br />\n識做AO稅局點會去做狗"},{"pid":"92c0169ec8d7f85c6af962b33f9cde451a76479a","tid":1399723,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:21:55.000Z","msg":"你真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d932f49239d111d425330c2d6951951b672acd0","tid":1399723,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:22:29.000Z","msg":"唔可以 因為毅進唔識英文<br />\n一封信都睇唔明點做野？"},{"pid":"9bcc6f799530aa1db04d29b605298de967e35a5d","tid":1399723,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"警察已經接管左香港啦 你都on撚9"},{"pid":"850f836b4c7246890dead1049f716b2e13dd023c","tid":1399723,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:25:46.000Z","msg":"坐counter"},{"pid":"001945a1a27368a56479d3930b5afb826ad2c47b","tid":1399723,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"850f836b4c7246890dead1049f716b2e13dd023c","tid":1399723,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl